<typeStatus box="[999,1095,1563,1586]" pageId="4" pageNumber="391">holotype</typeStatus>
, to acknowledge his achievements in the study of the Afrotropical 
<taxonomicName box="[824,908,1595,1618]" class="Insecta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Diptera</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
